# Assets Loans And Advances Including Accrued Interest Net Provisions Impairment And Deferred Fee Income Amount

## identifier
de7536

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for the principal amount of loans and advances provided, including any accrued interest, net of associated provisions for impairment and deferred fee income. Loans and advances are those financial assets measured at the appropriate valuation method and categorised as "Loans and receivables" in the relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndAdvancesIncludingAccruedInterestNetProvisionsImpairmentAndDeferredFeeIncome.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
